      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Dependable & Well-Maintained \u2013 Ready to Hit the Road! \ud83d\ude97 Here's a genuinely solid car at a fair, honest price! This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly, has been cared for, and looks presentable inside and out. You'll find the usual signs of everyday use (minor wear here and there), but nothing that takes away from its reliability or enjoyment. If you're looking for a trustworthy daily driver without paying premium prices, this is a smart pick. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
