    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Here's a fantastic opportunity to get into a solid, dependable vehicle that's ready to hit the road! This car presents in good condition \u2014 the exterior shows only minor signs of normal wear, and the interior is clean and comfortable with everyday use evident but well-maintained. Mechanically, it's running well and has been cared for, making it a reliable choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures. If you're looking for a great value without the premium price tag of a mint-condition car, this one deserves a serious look!",
      "price": 35000.0,
